{"block1":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Honey makes drinks more delicious. If you combine honey with your tea, your tea will have a&nbsp;subtle, sweet taste In fact, honey is the exception to the notion that sweet things aren&#39;t good for you. Actually, honey has a lot of health benefits that you will&nbsp;greatly appreciate.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/portrait-of-a-woman-with-bottle-of-honey.jpg\" class=\"img_right \" alt=\"portrait of a woman with bottle of honey\" style=\"float: right; padding: 8px; padding-right: 0;\" \/>&nbsp;Honey boosts the immune system. It has <a href=\"http:\/\/www.webmd.com\/food-recipes\/antioxidants-topic-overview\"  >antioxidant<\/a> and anti-bacterial properties that make the body stronger. To benefit from this, mix a spoonful of honey with your tea or lemon juice in the morning.<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Honey is a good remedy for a&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/www.mayoclinic.org\/diseases-conditions\/yeast-infection\/basics\/causes\/con-20035129\"  >yeast infection<\/a>, and is also good for cuts and burns.<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Honey is good for those who can&rsquo;t sleep. Try mixing a teaspoon of honey with a glass of milk before going to bed.<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Honey is said to be anti-cancer. It has properties that can prevent carcinogens.<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Honey is&nbsp;a good energy booster. In fact, it is recommended to take 1 teaspoon of honey before working out. The same goes for those who feel tired in the morning and are in need of extra boost to face the day.<\/li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Honey with garlic is also used to treat asthma. Many people have tried this and&nbsp;seen great results.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You see, honey doesn&rsquo;t only taste good in itself, and make food and drinks taste even better;&nbsp;it also promotes good health for everyone!<\/p>\r\n"}